topProducts.name: Cauliflower Wings
quotes: The cauliflower wings were fantastic, and the ranch dipping sauce was so good that I’d come back just to have it again with fries
topProducts.description: Crispy cauliflower florets served as a plant-based alternative to chicken wings, often accompanied by dipping sauces.
topProducts.whyPeopleLoveIt: Customers praise them for being fantastic and amazing, with a particularly noteworthy ranch dipping sauce.

topProducts.name: Dirty Secret Burger
quotes: Burger was served wet with sauce. A little dab will do ya. Wife struggled to eat the burger.
The chickin’ burger didn’t hit the spot for me
topProducts.description: A signature plant-based burger. While one review mentions a 'chickin' burger', another complains about a burger being too wet with sauce.
topProducts.whyPeopleLoveIt: It is a signature item mentioned on the website, though reviews suggest execution can be inconsistent, with some finding it overly saucy.

topProducts.name: SoyClone / Frostbites
quotes: We got the frostbites, which are a thicker version of a milkshake. I wasn’t such a fan of these either, they tasted a little chemically to me.
I look forward to returning for the popular shakes and more!
topProducts.description: A thick, plant-based milkshake dessert, also referred to as a Frostbite. Mentioned as a popular item.
topProducts.whyPeopleLoveIt: They are noted as a popular item and a thicker version of a traditional milkshake, though one customer found the taste to be 'chemically'.

topProducts.name: Cake
quotes: the carrot cake was rich and delicious
The cake we had was good at least.
We shared the buffalo “chicken” wrap, chopped cheese steak and chocolate cake. All vegan. Absolutely delicious!
topProducts.description: The restaurant offers various cakes, including carrot and chocolate varieties. All are vegan.
topProducts.whyPeopleLoveIt: The cakes are consistently praised as being rich, delicious, and a satisfying part of the meal.

topProducts.name: Steak Sandwich
quotes: Steak sandwich was burned beyond acceptable crisp. Tasted like ash.
We shared the buffalo “chicken” wrap, chopped cheese steak and chocolate cake. All vegan. Absolutely delicious!
topProducts.description: A plant-based steak-style sandwich, also referred to as a chopped cheese steak.
topProducts.whyPeopleLoveIt: Reception is mixed; one customer called it delicious while another received one that was severely burnt.

topProducts.name: Buffalo 'Chicken' Wrap
quotes: The chicken bacon ranch wrap was perfect and would be great with some extra sauce for dipping.
I also found the buffalo wrap too heavy the time before. Lots of soy curls and sauce and not a lot of veggies to cut through all of the heaviness.
topProducts.description: A wrap filled with plant-based 'chicken' (soy curls) and buffalo sauce. A chicken bacon ranch version is also mentioned.
topProducts.whyPeopleLoveIt: One customer found the chicken bacon ranch version 'perfect', while another felt the buffalo version was too heavy on sauce and soy curls without enough vegetables.
